      "id": "09bc38fc-bd25-40e6-b1e8-6bb75defaf5a",
      "name": "Architecture",
      "type": "n8n-nodes-base.stickyNote",
      "typeVersion": 1,
      "position": [
        -20,
        2880
      ],
      "parameters": {
        "content": "# System Architecture\n\n```\nCLIENT PORTAL (Next.js + Supabase)\n  /portal/advisory/* — Client dashboard, meetings, tasks, documents, pricing\n  /admin/advisory/*  — Adviser pipeline, compliance, analytics\n  /api/advisory/*    — 14 REST endpoints with role-based access\n\nDATABASE (Supabase PostgreSQL)\n  16 fa_* tables | Row-Level Security | Audit triggers\n  3 RPC functions | Storage bucket for documents\n\nINTEGRATIONS\n  Microsoft: Outlook Email + Calendar + Teams Meetings + Graph API Transcripts\n  WhatsApp: Cloud API template messages (confirmations, reminders)\n  AI: OpenRouter -> Claude Sonnet (briefings, transcripts, compliance, research)\n  Airtable: Operational dashboards (pipeline, metrics, compliance log)\n```\n\n**Compliance:** FAIS Act (Record of Advice, Fee Disclosure) + POPIA (Consent Management, Data Protection)\n\n**Multi-Tenant:** Each advisory firm isolated by firm_id across all tables",
        "width": 1480,
        "height": 420,
        "color": 5
      }
    }
